==English==
===Verb===
'''[[knock]] [[on]] [[wood]]'''
#{{idiom}} An action taken or referred to [[ward off]] some misfortune that is discussed but has not happened yet.
#:''I do a lot of walking, and I have never had any knee problems yet, '''knock on wood'''.''

